::Spears::
Then rubbled was starting to fall in on it'sself.  She closed her 
eyes as some scraps of the wall the was leaning against the table 
started to bow down and snapped, falling and hitting her in the 
face.  She now had a cut along side her cheek.  She could taste the 
mech fluid in her mouth.  She sceamed out again, hoping that someone 
would hear her.  "HEEEEELLLLP!"  She then thought she heard voices 
outside.  She screamed again, "HEY!HEY!I"M UNDER HERE! HELP! HELP 
ME!"  She cursed under her breath.  She would get that maximal that 
left here in the ark to die.  She couldn't believe that she had gone 
from being a warrior and reduced to being left to die under a rubbish 
pile.  She screamed again and again.  She prayed that the voices she 
was hearing were not something invented from her imagination.
